♪Candle lights the halls
through springs and autumns♪

275
00:14:36,735 --> 00:14:41,984
♪Love and hate
are written in a few strokes♪

276
00:14:43,462 --> 00:14:45,733
♪Imperishable♪

277
00:14:47,871 --> 00:14:50,912
♪Bloodstained vows
with a touch of tenderness♪

278
00:14:51,775 --> 00:14:57,344
♪Fate is written by the universe♪

279
00:14:58,292 --> 00:15:01,402
♪Unending♪

280
00:15:02,624 --> 00:15:03,456
♪Heaven falls♪

281
00:15:03,616 --> 00:15:06,084
♪No concern for cause and effect♪

282
00:15:06,416 --> 00:15:07,200
♪On the throne♪

283
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:09,904
♪Is it a shackle♪

